Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可不算是最令人振奮的副總統人選吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is not the most inspiring choice for a vice president, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}瑞秋·麥多秀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的確是位備受尊敬的官員  務實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I mean, a well-respected operator. Pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但老實說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But let's face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也許只是總統對國會的示好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is probably just a nod to Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提拔一名議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tapping one of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次大選前  他也就是個充數的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's really nothing more than a placeholder until 2016, assuredly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對他私下宣誓就職毫不驚訝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not surprised he's doing a private swearing-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜總統是想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My bet is that the president wants to draw
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘量保持低調\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as little attention to this as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這其中實在沒什麼讓人...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's just no real wow fa--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Christina's working out well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在適應  不過我目前挺滿意的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's getting her sea legs, but I've been happy so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很勤奮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She works hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她能替我陪總統出行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a big load off my shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是大大鬆了一口氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when she can travel with the president instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我留在這邊更有用武之地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I get so much more done when I stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統有看好的黨鞭人選嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president have a preference in the whip's race?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到局面會變得這麼不堪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can't believe how ugly it's gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人無比失望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was more disappointing than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當心  是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Watch out. Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒打擾你們吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I hope I'm not interrupting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是不一般\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安保要求  他們得趕工  小心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Security specs. They had to work fast. Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡簡直像戰場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's like a war zone around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改建的目的就是隔絕外界影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The idea is to keep the war from getting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黨鞭的競爭怎麼樣了  議員先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How's the whip's race coming, congressman?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.04,0:01:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和霍華德的競爭蠻激烈的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's tight between you and Howard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這你得問他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well you'd have to ask Howard,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他大概在忙著琢磨怎麼搞我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if he's not too busy trying to sodomize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去打個招呼吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shall we go and say hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  別逼我跟他說話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For god sakes, don't make me talk to that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  霍華德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good to see you, Howard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見到你真高興  韋斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nice to see you, Wes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興個屁啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I bet it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-鮑勃  -弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Bob. - Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你邀請我  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Appreciate you inviting me, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什麼  -謝謝你邀請我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- What? - Thanks for inviting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}總統及副總統宣誓就職時需由最高法院首席法官見證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有換衣服的地嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there somewhere I can go to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有  大廳那邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, absolutely. There's room down the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  照應一下法官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug, will you take care of the judge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他準備好了就趕緊開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And when he's ready, let's get this thing over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫大家進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll start bringing 'em in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自願承擔此義務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...that I take this obligation freely,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既無保留  也不逃避\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without any mental reservation or purpose of evasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自願承擔此義務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...that I take this obligation freely,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既無保留  也不逃避\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without any mental reservation or purpose of evasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將盡職盡責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that I will well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離總統只差一步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One heartbeat away from the presidency,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻不用一張選票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and not a single vote cast in my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民主也不過如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Democracy is so overrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成我的本職工作  上帝保佑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...office on which I am about to enter, so help me God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將盡職盡責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that I will well and faithfully discharge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成我的本職工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the duties of the office on which I am about to enter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so help me god.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Congratulations, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我們繼續治理國家吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, let's get back to running the country.
