Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們中一人將接任黨鞭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, one of you is gonna replace me as the whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆最有希望  大家也知道你們都想爭取\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're the two frontrunners, and we know you both want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你們一點領導風範也沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you're not behaving like men who belong in the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,場面話就別說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to tone down the rhetoric.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們傷及了黨派利益\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're hurting your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在迴應霍華德拋出的謊言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm just responding to the lies Howard's been slinging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公費出遊是真事  韋斯  不是我編的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those junkets happened, Wes. I'm not making it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你任人唯親呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And nepotism's any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那不是事實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's just not true, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你妹夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And your sister's husband
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是湊巧被任命為財務部長了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}just happened to be appointed state treasurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前妹夫  是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ex-husband. And yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一派胡言  霍華德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That is such a load of crap, Howard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生們  鮑勃說的對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gentlemen, Bob is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倆的鬥爭一旦被曝光\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This sort of cat-fighting gets out in the press,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管誰贏  都不是好事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whichever one of you wins hits the ground limping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別出陰招了  大家文明一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's keep it clean and bring some civility back to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we agree to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倆握個手我會安心一些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd feel a lot better if you shook hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和他在一起呢  克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm with him right now, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了  我晚些時候去你辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm off. I'll swing by your office later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  還沒裝修好呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't. It's not ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這兒辦公了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be working from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tusk is in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他45分鐘後和總統會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's meeting with the president in 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜剛告訴我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Christina just told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商貿聯委會談判的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Joint Commission talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是這麼說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜還真有用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Christina is proving useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們隨時聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We stay in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給凱茜·杜蘭特打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get me Cathy Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的人要過來嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your people coming by?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有我的新辦公室主任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just my new chief of staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招人之前也沒有別人了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's all I've got until we hire more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做副總統的夫人什麼感覺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So how does it feel to be married to the vice president?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全一樣  就是有點吵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Exactly the same. Just louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國務卿杜蘭特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Secretary Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Congratulations, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你介紹國務卿  杜蘭特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}May I please introduce Secretary Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很榮幸  國務卿女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My pleasure, Madam Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直太意外了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is quite a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不知道你來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had no idea you were in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  總統閣下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱瑟琳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛好撞見了雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We just happened to run into Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話記錄肯定能證明我是對的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The phone records will absolutely prove I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有電話記錄  你知道的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There were no phone records. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還有運營商的資料歷史記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The data history with the carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新調查根本不可能  就算重新調查了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even if we got the case reopened, which isn't gonna happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道要拿到獲取運營商資料的令狀有多難嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}do you have any idea how hard it is to get a warrant for phone data?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合理理由\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Probable cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他找來進行訊問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bring him in for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚴格說這事在你轄區之內\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Technically you have jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國的副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vice president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你覺得這很荒謬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know this all sounds preposterous to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你好好看看我的筆記\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but if -- if you go through my notes --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就看過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've been through your notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽是聽了  但你根本沒聽進去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've listened. But you haven't heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是間接證據  但都合情合理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Circumstantial, yes. But plausible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你曾為更小的原因重新調查案子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you've reopened cases on less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必須停手了  哥們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This has gotta stop, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們說來說去就這麼幾句\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We keep having the same conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是意外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It can't be an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我給你看個東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. I'm gonna show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CNN想拿到這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}CNN tried to get a hold of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出於對家屬的尊重  我們拒絕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We eighty-sixed it out of respect to the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,監控錄影嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The footage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}加密檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看了肯定難受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not easy to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要麼是絆倒了  要麼是跳下去的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She tripped. Or jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是自殺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She didn't jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我逐幀放給你看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here it is, frame by frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩個目擊證人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, there were two witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個是患眼部黃斑變性的70歲老太太\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One was a 70-year-old woman with macular degeneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她什麼都沒看清楚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All she saw was a blur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二個就是車上的列車員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The second was the conductor of the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說看上去像是她摔倒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He said it looked like she fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了這兩個證人  就是監控錄影了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean between those two and this video, that's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看你可以看一萬遍  但是這個案子結了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can watch it a million times, but this case is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得把議程限制在幾個關鍵問題上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should limit the agenda to a couple of key issues:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工業製品的進口關稅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}import tariffs on industrial manufactured goods
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及稀土元素的出口限額\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and export quotas on rare earth elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們把這兩個都當做政治槓桿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're using both as political levers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也認為在這兩個問題上我們能有所進展\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I agree these are two areas where we can make meaningful progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我更擔心針對企業的網路攻擊的增加\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I'm worried about the rise in corporate cyber attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扯上這個就沒完了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a rabbit hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們早晚得說這件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we have to address it sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是我們要不要現在談這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's just a matter of whether we want to address it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國人不喜歡意外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Chinese don't like surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I'm proposing is that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在利用商貿聯委會談判委婉地提出這個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we use the Joint Commission talks to bring it up gently now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為下輪談判做好鋪墊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}set the stage for the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個商人  不是外交官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm a businessman, not a diplomat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是個在中國工作了35年的商人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I'm a businessman with 35 years experience working in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他們談判  不能太貪心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When they come to the table, you don't get greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在福建有一個合資煉油廠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're working on a co-venture refinery project in Fujian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是業內首家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which would be the first of its kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開了增加投資的渠道...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Open the gateway for increased investment --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路攻擊對那些合作企業構成威脅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cyber attacks threaten those co-ventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果中方可以通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's less a need for them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商業間諜活動獲取新技術  也就無需合作了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if the Chinese can obtain new technology from corporate espionage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克  你覺得呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更傾向於雷蒙德的想法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I lean more toward Raymond's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果引起中方的反感  那多年的努力都白費了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we antagonize the Chinese we could undo years of progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以低調行事  絕不會使強硬手腕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Allow me to do this quietly, with a soft touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會激怒他們  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't antagonize them, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們最不需要的就是自找麻煩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The last thing we want to do is rock the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎麼辦  凱瑟琳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you have in mind, Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建議性議程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A suggested agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是作為要求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not a demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事由中層出面  我根本不插手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll keep it mid-level. I won't get anywhere near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經表明瞭顧慮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've voiced my concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-要格外謹慎剋制  -我向你保證  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- A very soft touch. - You have my word, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德  一起吃個午餐吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond? Want to grab some lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之極\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  弗蘭克  歡迎加入白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Frank. Welcome to the West Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統就像曠野上的一棵孤樹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president is like a lone tree in an empty field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風往哪吹  他就往哪倒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He leans whichever way the wind is blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在雷蒙德·塔斯克的西風吹得實在太猛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And right now Raymond Tusk blows far too strong from the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是假髮嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is that a wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  他都留了好幾個月了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. He's been growing it out for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴安說她喜歡長髮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Diane says she likes it long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她  等她看到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I told her she'll feel differently
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他留起長髮辯就會改主意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}once she sees the first dread lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者聞到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or smells it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上週去看了你女兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I went to see your daughter last weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-想看看照片嗎  -好啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You want to see a picture? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她媽媽在嗎  -對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Was her mother there? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的錢夠用吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are they okay on money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格林伍茲的保險率費一月份要上調了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The rate at Greenwoods is going up in January.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱特琳娜擔心錢不夠用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Catalina is worried she's gonna be short.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會多打點去她賬上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure to put more into the account.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不舒服  我們不用聊她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't have to talk about her if you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不  沒事  我很感謝你去看她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no, no. It's fine. I appreciate you going to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  泰德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你邀我一起吃午餐  我以為你是想...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought that when you asked me to lunch it was because you want --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不  沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no, no. I mean, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想確保她們的需求都得到滿足\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to make sure they have what they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想找你談是為了...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the reason I wanted to talk --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛莉·塔特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lorrie Tate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛莉是我朋友  她怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lorrie's a friend of mine. What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說你有意競選黨鞭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She mentioned you're interested in the whip's race.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天吶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望她沒這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wish she hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為很荒唐啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because it's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是隨口說說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just mentioned it off-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韋斯和巴克沃特的競爭簡直...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The whole Webb and Buchwalter thing is just --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一團糟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Complete mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我是開玩笑的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你該認真想想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think you should be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想競選黨鞭嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有經驗啊  泰德  我還...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don’t have the experience, Ted. And I -- I --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將來再說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在  我沒有他們那樣的財力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But now I -- I don't have the money they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用我的錢  就有了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unless you use mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能把你的錢浪費在...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't waste your money on --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我找到那些還持觀望態度的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I funnel my PAC money to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我的政治行動委員會資金給他們一些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}some folks who are on the fence,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你正式宣佈前  拉攏一些支持者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}round up a couple dozen commitments before you announce,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你立刻就是有力競爭者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that would make you an instant contender.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說這是浪費嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now tell me that's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是千百萬啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're talking hundreds of thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是聖誕禮物  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not a Christmas present, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是黨鞭  我就在領導層有了堅定的盟友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}With you as whip I have a strong ally in the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的獲益不比你少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I stand to gain as much as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等片刻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hang on one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道哪裡...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know where the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  他信了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How did it go? Did he buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你給他吹了什麼風  吹得很到位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever bug you put in his ear burrowed deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單  那人喜歡你  對你視如己出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was easy. The man adores you like you're his own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你可得選我做首席副黨鞭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you sure as hell better make me Chief Deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得先當選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to win first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和泰德兩票  還剩111票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ted and I make two. 111 to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副黨鞭會數數總是好事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's always good when the Chief Deputy knows her arithmetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別扯淡  我們數票吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fuck off. Let's start taking names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個還不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This one seems promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康納·埃利斯  可靠  有經驗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Connor Ellis. He's solid. Good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他解決了瓊斯參議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, he's the one that got Senator Jones out of that mess
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}借調查名義影響民意的民意調查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推手民調的爛攤子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with the push polling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  免受紀律委員會的調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. Kept him from the ethics committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面試一下吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's set up an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我安排一下日程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll find a good time in schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們說說日程的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's talk about the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好挑一下我該參加哪些活動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think we need to be more selective with the events I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些是上任副總統夫人沒去成的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some of these are leftovers from Mrs. Matthews.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想取消也可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can cancel whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫要為兩位新晉海軍陸戰隊將軍授銜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your husband will be pinning stars on two newly commissioned Marine generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個你應該去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think that's one you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我介紹一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. Walk me through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位將軍分別是艾莉西婭·漢普頓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The generals are Alicia Hampton
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和道頓·麥金尼斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and Dalton McGinnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6點50到場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Arriving at 6:50 --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道頓·麥金尼斯嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dalton McGinnis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  認識嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大學同學\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We went to college together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛說到哪了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Arrive what time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6點50\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}6:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  出席人員名單給我一份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Great. I'd like a list of all the people that will be attending.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被排除在外沒什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not that big a deal if I get left out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你是國務卿啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you're the secretary of state.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克怎麼能參與決策\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, Tusk should not be determining policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有總統可以決定你該怎麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president alone should instruct you on what you are to pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們什麼關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's their relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直給總統出謀劃策\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's had his ear for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提建議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}An advisor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更像是導師  總統很重視他的建議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More of a mentor. And one whose advice is not easily dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還會繼續要求忽視網路戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's gonna keep pushing back on cyber warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非我給提上議程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not if I get it on the agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你提上議程他更會來勁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, especially if you get it on the agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商貿聯委會談判再度開啟時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tusk is not gonna take any chances
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克絕不會冒絲毫風險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when the next Joint Commission talks come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛不是支援他嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You agreed with him in the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們站一邊  他的態度只會更強硬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we had ganged up, he would have taken a firmer position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:14:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For all we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在就在勸總統改主意呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he's convincing the president right now to change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們絕不能給他機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now we need to remove that option as a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次談判時  強迫中方迴應網路安全問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Force the Chinese to confront the issue now, this round of talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答應總統不採取強硬手段的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I promised the president a soft touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能有意食言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't intentionally break my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是無意的呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What if it was unintentional?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱茜  如果你不喜歡現在的局勢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cathy, if you don't like how the table is set,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就乾脆攪局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}turn over the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你偷吸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有  是電子煙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I'm not. It's vapor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也算\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Still.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該試試\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會上癮  但沒副作用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Addiction without the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己抽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不睡嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You staying up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明晚的授銜儀式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This ceremony tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非我必須去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜歡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I hate these sorta things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這是副總統的首次亮相\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it is my first public appearance as vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要把這兒改成辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Should we turn this into a proper office?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊  樓下沒有私密性\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not a bad idea. No privacy downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找裝修隊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll talk to the contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Goodnight, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  先生  根據國會議事錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir! Sir! Congressional Record.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要談到六點嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Weren't the talks supposed to go until six?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不聽  我們談不下去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't talk if they won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中方不談了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did the Chinese walk out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經表明  除非他們肯談政府資助的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We made it clear that we won't discuss any other issues
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路攻擊  否則其他問題免談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}until government-sponsored cyber attacks are on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯然他們不開心了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Apparently that's not what they wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中方代表離席之前你說了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, what did you tell the Chinese delegation before they walked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒派人去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We didn't have anybody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商貿聯委會談判通常很無聊的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Joint Commission is usually a snooze-fest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not today it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經讓格里爾去弄了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've got Greer on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是國際板塊的新聞嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Isn't this international?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要寫網路戰的背景資料\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need somebody from the tech beat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得請科技板塊的記者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if we want any background on cyber warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他找到人接受署名採訪了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does he have anybody on record yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中方不肯談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Chinese aren't talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國代表團的話美聯社都報道了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And all the U.S. delegation said is what's in the AP wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何兩小時內網上要出報道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want something online in the next two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本週內發一篇深入後續報道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In-depth follow-up sometime this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡斯  你還好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, Lucas? You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還穿著昨天穿的那身\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're wearing the same clothes you wore yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你私生活發生了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know what's going on in your personal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎已經影響到你的工作了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but it seems to be entering the workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儀表很重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Appearances matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的編輯不能比他的記者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we can't have an editor looking more disheveled
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不修邊幅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than his reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩小時  一定給你個交待\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two hours. You'll have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道傑姬·夏普要競選黨鞭嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you know Jackie Sharp's running for Whip?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  這是我第一次聽說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, this is the first I'm hearing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟韋伯說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I spoke to Webb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛莉·塔特給他發了一封關於我的電郵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He got an email from Lorrie Tate about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴夫·霍蘭德給我發了一封關於他的電郵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got one from Dave Holland about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我不管\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which means nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:18:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公費旅遊  任人唯親  塔特跟夏普很親密\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The junkets, the nepotism. Tate and Sharp are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德跟她在退伍軍人事務委員會共事過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Holland serves on the VA committee with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她找別人出手  好撇清干係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She used proxies to insulate herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得是她把料爆給了他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you think that she gave the dirt to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  她在耍我們兩個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. She's been playing both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得她能拉到多少支持者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many commitments do you think she could have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前也就20個左右吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Around 20 so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那她還是被你倆遠遠甩在後面啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So she's a distant third.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她在一個個動搖我們的支持者啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But she's picking people off us left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得幫我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我支援你啊  韋斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have my support, Wes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就公開表態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then make that public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我公開支援你  博奇就會支援韋伯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I come out for you, Birch comes out for Webb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那反倒會害你  而不是幫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's gonna hurt you, not help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況很不妙  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is serious, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰德·哈維梅耶在贊助她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ted Havemeyer is bankrolling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想過跟傑姬談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you thought of talking to Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  原則上我不能那麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no. I can't do that on principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會跟哈維梅耶支援的人合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anyone who Havemeyer is backing, I don't work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我競選參議員的時候  他也攪了我的局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He pulled the same crap on me when I ran for Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他贊助我的主要對手  混蛋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He financed my primary opponent. Asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那由你決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that is your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你要讓舊賬阻礙你的競選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if you're gonna let an old grudge get in the way of progress --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不能這麼做  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just can't do it, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈維梅耶這些年一直想把我趕下去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Havemeyer's been trying to shove me down the totem pole for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓他得逞的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't give him the satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我尊重你  但這樣我就無能為力了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I can respect that, but my hands are tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事很微妙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a delicate matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們正在和中國政府溝通\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but we are in communication with the Chinese government
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何推進談判\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as to how to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不是表示美國將在網路攻擊的事上屈服\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does this mean the U.S. will back down on cyber attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國從不屈服\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The United States never backs down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是在重要問題上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}particularly on issues that are high priority to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國務卿女士  您是怎麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Madam Secretary, what did you--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是怎麼跟代表團團長說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What did you tell the head of the delegation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代表團越界了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The delegation overstepped its bounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但凱茜不能坑她自己的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but Cathy couldn’t throw her own people under the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她公開發表言論前該先跟我們商量一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She should have consulted us first before speaking publicly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媒體堵在她家門口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The press was on her doorstep
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統又在地球另一端\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the president was in another hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在批評她的做法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, look, I'm not condemning what she did,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她總得採取措施\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but she had to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她憑直覺做決定  並採取了行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She made a gut call and she acted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱們得撇清關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to distance ourselves from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統什麼時候回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When is the president back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能安排一次會面嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we set up a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱茜得公開道歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cathy needs to publicly apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能讓她跟總統談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we get her in the room with the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不應該先統一一下步調嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't we all be on the same page first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再想想辦法吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿吃的之前  你問我了一個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, you asked me a question before I went and got my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生  我是麥金尼斯將軍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President. General McGinnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不勝榮幸  希望你不介意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's a great honor. I hope you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統也想出席  他讓我代為參加\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president wishes he could be here. He's asked me to fill in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,榮幸的是我  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The honor is mine, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍  這是我妻子  克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And, General, this is my wife, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興見到你  克萊爾  好久不見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's good to see you, Claire. It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈佛的同學\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Harvard. We were classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾沒提過這事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire didn't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還約會過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We dated for a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有五分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}About five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  不打擾你們用餐了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anyway, I'll let you get back to your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我想起來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you. I've remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思的是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Interestingly enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南卡羅萊納州第一大作物不是棉花\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in South Carolina the largest crop is not cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是菸草\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It's tobacco.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三大作物是大麻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the third-largest crop is marijuana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱心裡明白就好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now -- we'll just keep that to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you all excuse me for just a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-只有她一個嗎  -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Is she alone? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想單獨談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you give us a few moments, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大一那年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Freshman year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事...是麥金尼斯嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean... McGinnis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯  弗蘭西斯  別做傻事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis, Francis. Please, don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會給他授銜...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am not gonna pin a medal on that --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必須授銜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  不能讓他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just a minute, please! There is no way that man --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  典禮要開始了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, they want to start the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一會兒  他不配接受...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just a minute, please! He does not deserve a medal..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯  求你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis. I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你  槍斃他都不過分\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm telling you, that man deserves to be taken out and shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不行  -求你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- No. - Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不要  -別...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- No. - Do not --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說等等\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  別惹事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do not make a scene. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆  謝謝你能來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tom. Thanks for coming by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走進來時  我以為會有一絲懷念\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, I thought I would miss this place the moment I stepped inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.87,0:22:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝斯黛拉沒問題吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hope you like Stella.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Beers up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How are things?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯  還不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're good. They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你開心嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒開心過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I haven't been happy a day in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在有時間了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I have time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以思考  寫作  我最近在構思小說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To think. To write. Been working on a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純粹是狗屁  不過還湊合\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's absolute shit. That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的  湯姆  真挺好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's great, Tom. That's really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找我來不是敘舊的吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you didn't ask me here just to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.63,0:23:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克·安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我萬分榮幸地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}On the president's behalf
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代表總統  授予艾莉西婭·漢普頓將軍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it is my great honor to formerly recognize the selection
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美軍歐洲司令部\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of General Alicia Hampton as Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令一職\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}United States European Command,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,授予道頓·麥金尼斯將軍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and General Dalton McGinnis
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國戰略司令部司令一職\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as Commander of the United States Strategic Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位模範領袖為美國海軍陸戰隊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The United States Marine Corps has been well served
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做出了卓越貢獻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by these two exemplary leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統與我希望兩位再接再厲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president and I are grateful for their continued service.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.64,0:24:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我瘋了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think I'm insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.28,0:24:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得你瘋了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think you're insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.11,0:24:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是經歷了太多痛苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think you've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.30,0:24:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想探個究竟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Trying to make sense of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.57,0:24:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我是對的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.21,0:24:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure I believe you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.67,0:24:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒駕的事的確是他掩蓋的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a fact that he helped cover up the DUI.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.89,0:24:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你手下的記者拿著這事來找你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Imagine if one of your reporters came to you with this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.32,0:24:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會登出去嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Could you print a word of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.26,0:24:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會  但會要求他們繼續調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, but I'd have them keep digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.95,0:25:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.63,0:25:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑心而論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you're honest with yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.06,0:25:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會說這故事太牽強了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}wouldn't you tell them it seemed farfetched?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.53,0:25:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,筆記說明不了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your notes aren't convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.58,0:25:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方報告也證實不了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The police reports don't prove a link.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.34,0:25:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-還有你的妄加猜測  -我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- And the speculative leaps you're making... - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.50,0:25:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,律人要先律己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hold yourself to the same standards as you hold your staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.26,0:25:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當時在和佐伊約會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You and Zoe were seeing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.23,0:25:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是猜的  也許錯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I'm assuming. Maybe I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.04,0:25:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在約會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We -- we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.19,0:25:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一任妻子去世時  我也接受不了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I lost my first wife, it didn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.41,0:25:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會在31歲就死於乳腺癌呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who dies of breast cancer at 31?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.33,0:25:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起訴  告醫生  醫院  所有人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted to sue. Doctors, the hospital, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.39,0:25:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得他們在隱瞞什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thought they were hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.10,0:25:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.47,0:26:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷讓人想要答案  但有時真的就沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Grief demands an answer, but sometimes there isn't one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.60,0:26:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能挽救她  就是這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Her life couldn't be saved. Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.77,0:26:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.25,0:26:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願找人談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you consider seeing someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.72,0:26:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛西婭去世時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a therapist who helped me a great deal
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.81,0:26:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個醫生幫了我很多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when Cynthia passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.85,0:26:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以幫你聯繫...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can put you in touch --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.45,0:26:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了  我不用見誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I don't need to see somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.51,0:26:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lucas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.84,0:26:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很感謝你過來  湯姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I appreciate you coming by, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.95,0:26:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也謝謝你的啤酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks for the beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.51,0:26:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時聯繫我吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You call me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.49,0:26:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照顧好自己  盧卡斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You take care of yourself, Lucas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.88,0:27:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還打算去哪嗎  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any plans to go elsewhere, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.42,0:27:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了  我們今晚不出去了  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. We're in for the night. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.48,0:27:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.76,0:27:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我累了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.17,0:28:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要什麼嗎  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you need something, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.61,0:28:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的遙控手柄  我想玩遊戲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, my remote. I want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.29,0:28:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.17,0:28:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.01,0:28:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路出問題了嗎  我上不了線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there something wrong with the Internet? I can't get online.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.03,0:28:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們封掉了連線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We had to disable the access.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個連線不安全\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not a secure connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.29,0:28:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我單獨待會兒嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Could you just give me a moment, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.20,0:28:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要您在外面  身邊就得有人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whenever you're out here, somebody needs to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.14,0:29:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在自家後院都不能獨自待著嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't be alone in my own backyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.26,0:29:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了算倒可以  但我說了不算\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If it were up to me, sir. But it's not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.91,0:29:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  密查姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.86,0:30:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我不想摔東西嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think I don't want to smash things?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.78,0:30:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的憤怒是你無法想象的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know what that anger is more than you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.30,0:30:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他壓著我的時候...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When he was on top of me --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.71,0:30:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不需要說這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't have to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.98,0:30:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.81,0:30:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他壓著我的時候  我使勁推\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When he was on top of me, I pressed my hand --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.17,0:30:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用盡全力推他的臉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with everything I could I pressed it into his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.72,0:30:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我使足了勁  弄傷了他的鼻子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I pressed it so hard I broke his nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.11,0:30:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那沒能阻止他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That didn't stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.98,0:30:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把床單塞進我嘴裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He shoved the sheets in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.78,0:30:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幾乎無法呼吸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I could barely breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.70,0:30:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次我想起那個女孩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Every time I think of her
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.81,0:30:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被人那樣按倒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}pinned down like that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.97,0:30:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都會勒死她  弗朗西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I strangle her, Francis,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.19,0:31:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣她才不會勒死我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so she doesn't strangle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.78,0:31:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須那樣  我們必須那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to. We have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.12,0:31:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The alternative is --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.86,0:31:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法忍受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's unlivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.10,0:31:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該休息了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.25,0:31:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道能不能睡著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.44,0:31:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就回樓下去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then you should go back downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.91,0:31:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早晨的時候  恨意也不會消退\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll still feel the hate in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.00,0:31:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會利用那份恨意  但不是去報復他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll use that. But not on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.73,0:32:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底說了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What did you communicate, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.69,0:32:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他提出議事日程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I told him to bring up the agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.32,0:32:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指出戰略對話的關鍵點  但別提要求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}suggest bullet points for the SED, but make no demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.41,0:32:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼會被理解成最後通牒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And how did that translate into a direct ultimatum?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.68,0:32:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時我的代表會探究言外之意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, sometimes my delegates try to read between the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.04,0:32:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們知道我為外交目的需要合理推卸責任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They know that I need plausible deniability for diplomatic purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.79,0:32:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼沒有立刻否認\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why didn't you immediately recant?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.20,0:32:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就我跟中國人打交道的經驗看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In my experience with the Chinese,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.96,0:32:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變卦會讓他們覺得我們軟弱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}backpedaling makes us look weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.56,0:32:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時有兩個選擇  丟臉或展示實力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had two choices: Lose face or exhibit strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.57,0:32:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇了後者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I chose the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.49,0:32:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  凱瑟琳  我會很快跟你聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, Catherine. I'll be in touch shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.85,0:32:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.15,0:32:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的私人線路打給雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get me Raymond on the private line.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.43,0:32:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得她是故意越界的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you think she overstepped on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.69,0:33:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱茜絕不會違反你的指令  不會故意違反\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cathy would never disobey your orders. Not on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.02,0:33:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德  弗蘭克在我這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond, I've got Frank here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.64,0:33:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就我們三個嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just the three of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.91,0:33:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就三個  早上好  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just us three. Morning, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.90,0:33:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在北京的聯繫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My contacts in Beijing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.30,0:33:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說商務部部長很激動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}tell me the minister of commerce is in a tizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.15,0:33:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想以此為藉口重拳出擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wants to use this as an excuse to start clenching fists.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.21,0:33:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要麼拆凱茜的臺  要麼支援她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, either I turn my back on Cathy or I stand behind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.86,0:33:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選前者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's gotta be the former.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.95,0:33:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.01,0:33:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不道歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you don't apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.18,0:33:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不是小矛盾  而是大摩擦了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you go from ruffling feathers to plucking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.87,0:33:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國人絕不會忍氣吞聲  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the Chinese won't stand for that, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.19,0:33:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是我跟內閣之間意思傳達有錯誤如何\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about perceived miscommunication between me and my cabinet?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.81,0:33:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生  現在的目標是繼續談判\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, right now the goal is to resume the talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.65,0:33:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就別擔心他們是怎麼想的了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't worry about perceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.33,0:33:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克沒錯  我們得現實點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank is right. We need to be pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.67,0:33:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先別擔心場面上的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Worry about appearances later.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.95,0:33:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  我讓凱瑟琳擬一份致歉信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. I'll have Catherine draft an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.07,0:33:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  必須由你親自寫  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, it has to come from you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.77,0:33:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道歉要有份量\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the apology is to mean anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.17,0:33:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得由白宮出面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it must come from the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.88,0:33:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的確應該更有成效\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That is certainly the more likely to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.86,0:33:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  那我親自寫  謝謝  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fine. I'll do it then. Thank you, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.35,0:33:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  加勒特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.13,0:34:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到他仍然直呼總統的名字嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you hear how he still uses the president's given name?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.64,0:34:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而沃克也毫不在意他的失敬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that Walker doesn't flinch at the lack of respect it implies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.10,0:34:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  恕我直言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, forgive me if this isn't the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.48,0:34:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有點猶豫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you seem a bit hesitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.16,0:34:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.86,0:34:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於公眾看法的事  你所言極是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you've raised a good point about public perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.30,0:34:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓你覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want you to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.05,0:34:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對你的擔憂毫不在意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm dismissing your concerns casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.82,0:34:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  你也擔心這個嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It's a concern for you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.46,0:34:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱茜提出的觀點不無道理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is some insight into what Cathy brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.89,0:34:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變卦就是軟弱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Backpedalling is weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.74,0:34:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟中國人合作總是碰運氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, it's always a coin toss with the Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.30,0:34:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有時候堅定立場比讓步妥協要好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But sometimes standing your ground is better than giving in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.09,0:34:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你強勢  他們反而更尊重你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They respect you more when you show strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.85,0:34:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你改變對此的看法了嗎  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you changing your mind on this, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.87,0:34:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得  你該按自己的心意決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just think it's important that you do what you think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.40,0:34:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國人民選你當總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The American people voted you president.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.99,0:34:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我  也不是雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not me. Not Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.36,0:34:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了再告訴你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll let you know what I decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.64,0:35:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.87,0:35:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得安德伍德會選她嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think she's Underwood's choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.30,0:35:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒直說  所以有可能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He deflected, so it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.32,0:35:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得合作  韋斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we need to work together on this, Wes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.95,0:35:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則我們倆都得完蛋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Before we both get screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.40,0:35:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.77,0:35:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們中一個人退出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One of us drops out,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.16,0:35:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支援另一個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}throws support to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.81,0:35:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就能削弱她的支援力量\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That'll dwarf any following she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.43,0:35:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我退出嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want me to drop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.84,0:35:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定任命你做眾議院撥款委員會主席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure you get my chairmanship on appropriations.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.82,0:35:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你至多能任命我做紀律委員會主席  這沒人稀罕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All you can offer me is, uh, Ethics, which nobody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.48,0:35:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們把事定下來吧  韋斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's put this to bed, Wes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.47,0:36:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韋伯肯定跟他談了協議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Webb must have offered him a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.24,0:36:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就提出更好的條件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then we have to offer a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.68,0:36:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜是撥款委員會  我給不了更好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm guessing appropriations. There's no way I can top that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.46,0:36:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非是眾議院稅賦委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Except for ways and means.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.06,0:36:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓你把職位給巴克沃特這樣的混蛋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I -- I won't let you give your chair to an ass like Buchwalter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.85,0:36:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是黨鞭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you're the Whip,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.68,0:36:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你地位比他  和其他主席都高\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you outrank him and every other chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.94,0:36:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他的委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Screw committees.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.70,0:36:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能直接跟議長交流\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll have a direct line to the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.40,0:36:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別固執了  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't be stubborn, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.90,0:36:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他會接受嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think he'd take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.10,0:36:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他連韋伯的條件都願意接受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was willing to take a deal from Webb.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.11,0:36:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你是他最討厭的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you're the only person he hates more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.59,0:36:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很蠻人  但不是傻子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's a brute. But he's not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.64,0:36:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不是出於忠誠而拒絕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I know you're not refusing out of loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.83,0:36:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.56,0:36:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以是泰德的緣故\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So it's because of Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.69,0:36:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得自己很厲害  對吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think you are hot shit, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.70,0:36:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能放下架子  像成年人那樣談正經事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we set egos aside and talk business like the adults we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.93,0:37:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的不只是稅賦委員會主席之位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want more than ways and means.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.72,0:37:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.08,0:37:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要哈維梅耶走人  不只是退休\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want Havemeyer gone. Not just retired....
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.01,0:37:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他從政壇消失\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Politically dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.46,0:37:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,競選是12年前的事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That race was 12 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.24,0:37:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是他  我也能當12年參議員了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was 12 years I could have been in the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.42,0:37:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就想報復  真的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Revenge? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.99,0:37:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是報復\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.63,0:37:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是報應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Equity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.32,0:37:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你準備怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.54,0:37:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴克沃特不會讓步的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Buchwalter won't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.14,0:37:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這一生最鄙視小氣之人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, there's nothing I despise more in life than pettiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.19,0:37:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去找韋伯  但我給不了他什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I could approach Webb, but I don't have enough to offer him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.68,0:37:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不會退選的  他自尊心太強\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ah, he'd never drop out. Too much pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.70,0:37:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.44,0:37:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是泰德的檔案  他有個私生女\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is my file on Ted. An illegitimate daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.69,0:37:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和保姆生的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The nanny, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.17,0:37:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫艾米莉·羅德里格斯  19歲了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Her name is Emily Rodriguez. 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.13,0:37:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,患腦中風\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cerebral palsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.12,0:37:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道艾米莉的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know about Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.16,0:38:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們還在這裡討論什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, then why are we having this conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.72,0:38:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這說來話長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.01,0:38:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私生女  我沒看出有什麼複雜的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The daughter? It's very black and white to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.93,0:38:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟泰德是一輩子的交情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've known Ted since I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.83,0:38:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我父親是好友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He and my father were very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.40,0:38:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I'm aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.26,0:38:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直都對我關照有加\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's always looked out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.19,0:38:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把我送進西點軍校  資助我第一次競選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He got me into West Point. He funded my first race.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.11,0:38:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡泰德  他一直都很有團隊精神\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like Ted. He's always been a team player.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.10,0:38:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不幸  他擁有這樣的祕密\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's unfortunate he has this secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.12,0:38:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個錯誤  他一直都很後悔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was a mistake. One he's always regretted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.48,0:38:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她出生之後  他讓我去探望她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}After she was born he asked me to check in on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.46,0:38:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他自己做不到  而他信任我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because he couldn't. Because he trusted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.26,0:38:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.33,0:38:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來這裡的時候就知道你該做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You came in here knowing what you had to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.41,0:38:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你還是希望我能變個戲法  你就不用那麼做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}hoping I would pull a rabbit out of a hat so you wouldn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.52,0:38:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認識這姑娘  我認識她母親\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know the girl. I know her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.16,0:38:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們不該經受那種事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These people don't deserve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.63,0:38:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該支的招都支了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've given you all I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.13,0:38:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要如何決定是你自己的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever you decide is your prerogative.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.74,0:38:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也許我錯看了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But maybe I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.32,0:38:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰德對我來說就像家人一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ted is family to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.52,0:38:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用來取代親生女兒的養女\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}An adopted daughter in lieu of a real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.21,0:38:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  國務卿來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, the secretary is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.78,0:38:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  讓她進來  你下去吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you. Send her in. Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.95,0:39:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.63,0:39:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太長了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.67,0:39:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一點  但也還好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A little bit, but not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.02,0:39:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部分  三個段落\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This part, three paragraphs in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.24,0:39:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於電話公司嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, about the phone companies?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.53,0:39:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多跟我講講\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.25,0:39:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是國土安全部的主要擔憂之一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's one of Homeland Security's major concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.83,0:39:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路攻擊會滲透到電話運營商\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That the cyber attacks might infiltrate phone carriers,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.44,0:39:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到數百萬人的資料記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}get access to millions of people's data history.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.59,0:39:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如他們跟誰通過電話嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like who they called?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.68,0:39:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  跟誰通過電話  發過簡訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, who they called, texted,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.22,0:39:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡訊是什麼內容\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what they texted,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.76,0:39:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何時  何地  所有資訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when, where they were. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.28,0:39:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這種可能嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that's possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.93,0:39:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前沒有嚴重的資訊洩露事件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There haven't been any catastrophic breaches yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.33,0:39:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少沒有相關報道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At least not reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.44,0:39:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是中國似乎已經開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it looks like the Chinese are starting to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.88,0:39:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在深網上招募僱傭黑客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}recruit mercenaries on the Deep Web
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.52,0:39:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發動無法追蹤的網路游擊戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to launch guerilla-type attacks that can't be tracked back --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.39,0:39:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  深網  我聽說過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wait, wait, wait. Hold on. The Deep Web. I've heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.61,0:39:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.34,0:39:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,96%的網路內容無法通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, 96% of the internet isn't accessible
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.80,0:39:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通引擎搜索到  這其中大部分毫無價值\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}through standard search engines. Most of it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.98,0:39:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那裡你幾乎可以找到任何東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it's where you go to find anything and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.09,0:39:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兒童色情片  位元幣洗錢  郵購麻醉劑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Child porn, Bitcoin laundering, mail-order narcotics,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.46,0:39:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僱傭黑客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}hackers for hire.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.42,0:39:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼進入深網\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do you access it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.72,0:40:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實很簡單  你想看的話我可以演示\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's actually pretty easy. I could show you if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.69,0:40:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  我很好奇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.43,0:40:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mind if I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.06,0:40:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請便\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.49,0:40:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  首先你需要洋蔥路由\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, first thing you need is TOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.73,0:40:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人喜歡隱形網  但我覺得洋蔥路由更好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some people prefer I2P, but I think TOR is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.03,0:40:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洋蔥路由是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is TOR?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.46,0:40:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它可以通過代理伺服器保護你  讓你匿名\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It protects you through proxy servers. Keeps you anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.86,0:40:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我來演示如何進入\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I'll show you how to get to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.75,0:40:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,論壇和即時聊天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the posting boards and the IRCs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要提醒你  不要隨便亂點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I gotta warn you: Be careful what you click.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.35,0:40:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這上面有些很瘋狂的東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some crazy shit there, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.85,0:40:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長久以來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For too long, uh, we've, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.76,0:40:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們對網路戰一事小心翼翼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}danced on egg shells regarding the issue of cyber warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.44,0:40:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭特國務卿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, Secretary Durant
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.34,0:40:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是按照我的指令行事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}acted on instructions that came directly from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.48,0:40:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果中國沒有誠意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, if the Chinese are not willing to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.98,0:40:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行一場有意義的對話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}engage in a meaningful dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.45,0:40:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探討美國公司的智慧財產權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}about intellectual property of American corporations
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.29,0:40:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及對我政府網路設施的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as well as this deliberate targeting
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.65,0:40:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓄意攻擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of our government's online infrastructure,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.76,0:40:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就證明他們抱有一種雙重標準的心態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}well then that is proof of a double-standard mentality
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.44,0:40:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們將不再容忍這種心態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that we shall no longer tolerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.72,0:40:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們派往商貿聯合委員會的代表\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our delegation to the Joint Commission on Commerce and Trade
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.03,0:40:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遭到了美國政府代表的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}was unfairly accused and defamed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.03,0:41:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不公平指控與汙衊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by representatives of the United States government.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.80,0:41:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中華人民共和國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The People's Republic of China
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.97,0:41:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}will not be threatened
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.34,0:41:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒謬而未經證實的指控所脅迫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by derisive and unsubstantiated claims.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.91,0:41:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果白宮還要繼續如此行事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As long as the White House continues to behave this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.74,0:41:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼將來任何的雙邊對話都是不可能的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}any future bilateral trade talks will be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.43,0:41:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得大吃一驚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It caught me by surprise, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.30,0:41:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我掛電話之後  你又對他說什麼了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you say anything to him after I hung up yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.48,0:41:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  你跟他談過了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Have you spoken to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.33,0:41:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  幾分鐘前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.77,0:41:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他做了他認為該做的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He said he did what he thought was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.20,0:41:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我們沒法反駁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, there's nothing we can do to combat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.25,0:41:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一般不會招呼都不打\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He doesn't usually go against my advice
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.76,0:41:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就違揹我的建議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without giving me fair warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.36,0:41:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you suggesting, Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.40,0:41:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他容易受人操縱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's easily manipulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.39,0:41:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Clearly not in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.79,0:41:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這問題必須解決  就指望你了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to fix this. And I'm counting on you for that, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.46,0:41:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一遍  我不欠你什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me freshen your memory. I don't owe you any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.66,0:41:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答應跟你合作  不是給你賣力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I promised to work with you, not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.84,0:41:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於中國的問題  我們的目標一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And when it comes to China, we both want the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.11,0:41:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以得合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we need to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.56,0:41:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說服加勒特撤回言論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To convince Garrett he should retract.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.60,0:41:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是支援總統的選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To support the president in the path that he's chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.91,0:42:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可是在公然挑釁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}While he continues to antagonize them publicly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.75,0:42:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這是持續贏得民眾認可\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}While he continues to benefit from a bump in approval ratings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.86,0:42:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對中的強硬政策很吃香的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A tough stance on China is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.14,0:42:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點可以加以利用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we can use that to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.15,0:42:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐心點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's just be patient
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.21,0:42:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儘量暗中調解一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and see if we can smooth things over from back channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.28,0:42:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的耐心是有限的  儘快讓我看到成果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I don't see any results, you won't have my patience for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.42,0:42:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.98,0:42:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭特的話記得告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me know what Durant has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.66,0:42:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.60,0:42:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.38,0:42:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為他不會願意接受我的恩惠呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought he might balk at taking a handout from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.36,0:42:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是小恩小惠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd call it more than a handout.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.66,0:42:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他向來不難收買\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, he's always been the sort of man
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.74,0:42:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是代價一直很大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who could be bought, but never cheaply.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.83,0:42:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贏得他的不是主席位子  泰德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not the chairmanship that bought him, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.24,0:42:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.78,0:42:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在告訴你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm telling you this
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.71,0:42:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是給你時間跟你妻子談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so that you have time to call your wife
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.55,0:42:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且準備發言稿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and prepare your statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.07,0:43:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼脫身  他要幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's my out? What does he want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.45,0:43:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脫不了  他就想傷你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is no out. He wants it to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.56,0:43:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.41,0:43:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說可以辦到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just promised him that I could make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.52,0:43:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能這麼做  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't do this, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.26,0:43:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天報導就見報\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The story's breaking tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.27,0:43:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪部分\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What part of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.37,0:43:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不提名字  只說你有私生女\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No names. Just that you have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.22,0:43:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想沒想過對戴安的影響  對我們的兒子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you thought about what this will do to Diane? To our sons?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.51,0:43:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不覺得光彩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I hate myself for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.93,0:43:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我能撐過去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I'll get over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.13,0:43:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那她呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.04,0:43:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉  你連名字都不敢說嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Emily. You can't even say her name, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.33,0:43:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少教育我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't lecture me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.05,0:43:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都沒跟她共處過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've never been in the same room with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.93,0:43:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給她提供了最好的醫療條件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's had the best treatment available.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.25,0:43:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人  滿身的儀器連線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Alone. Hooked up to machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.02,0:43:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯之後就沒有護士了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Surrounded by nurses who punch out at dinnertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.24,0:43:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我有多難過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't know what I've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.45,0:43:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你  那她呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You? What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.48,0:43:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經盡力了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't do more than I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.13,0:43:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡說  泰德  你有辦法的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's bullshit, Ted. You could've found a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.64,0:43:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會向你為自己辯護\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't defend myself to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.44,0:43:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  跟你老婆說吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't. Save that for your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.53,0:44:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要懲罰你  泰德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This isn't to punish you, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.14,0:44:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比那簡單\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's -- it's simpler than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.72,0:44:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初我鼓勵你參選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I first encouraged you to run for office,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.71,0:44:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是覺得你不達目的不罷休\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's because I sensed how unstoppable you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.81,0:44:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可沒想到連我你都可以犧牲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I never thought I'd have to lie down on the tracks myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.75,0:44:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是想弄死我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you're going to put my neck in the noose,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.28,0:44:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動手時要看著我的眼睛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}look me in the eye while you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.74,0:44:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對我的付出我很感激\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm very grateful for all that you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.28,0:44:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能做個好黨鞭  傑奎琳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll make an excellent whip, Jacqueline.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.18,0:44:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾出我的辦公室吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now please get out of my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.73,0:44:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.38,0:45:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於清靜了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's finally quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.84,0:45:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.72,0:45:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是咱倆的堡壘了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have our fortress now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.76,0:45:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where are you coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.15,0:45:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新辦公室  今天剛裝修完\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My new office. They just finished setting it up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.56,0:45:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.50,0:45:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是間辦公室  湊合吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's an office. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.60,0:45:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}昵稱  Data_Crusader  主題  需要獲取通話記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.73,0:46:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}昵稱  Data_Crusader  主題  需要獲取通話記錄  內容  美國副總統
